seller.description:
Five years of passion for web development. I am a WordPress developer who can take care of your website from scratch to the advanced stage, from theme customizations with unique features.

I have worked for many people and companies. I have successfully built 250+ websites for all industries, from small and mid-level businesses to high-end companies.

If you're looking for a WordPress developer or SEO specialist, I'd love to chat with you. Please send me a message, and let's discuss your project!!

reviews.comment: I have been fortunate enough to have had great gigs on Fiverr, but Sohan truly stands out. He embodies relentlessness when it comes to problem-solving. While he might not respond to your questions immediately, rest assured it's because he's diligently working on a solution. He'll also send you a video explanation to ensure you understand his recommendations. And he doesn't just solve the problem. HE EXCEEDS EXPECTATIONS! Trust me, I've had some complex issues, so much so that two other Fiverr gigs couldn't resolve, but Sohan did. My recommendation? Give him a chance to tackle your challenges. He will deliver what he promises.

Collaborating with Sohan on the revamping of our website was excellent in every aspect. Despite the predefined content and look of the website, Sohan provided valuable insights and, with his creativity, contributed to a modern yet business-oriented appearance of the site. Throughout the collaboration, mutual trust was built, especially when Sohan identified potential additional needs, promptly addressing them within the agreed-upon time and budget. Sohan's offer to continue collaborating post-implementation to address any later identified requirements was also of significant importance. The user experience of working with Sohan has been extremely positive. Highly recommended!

He is a genius! He recovered my website in less than an hour (and I can assure you it was badly damaged.) He updated my website to be more secure. Suggested many tips for maintaining the website clean.

Sohan was amazing. From the beginning I explained that this was my first time publishing a website and he has been nothing but understanding, and patient. Sohan takes directions well and even provided suggestion based off the information given.
He was really helpful; he helped me apply and set up the web hosting and domain stuff, and he knew what they were doing. Sure to recommend him to anyone who needs website design and setup.
